{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"759beb4e-f21e-4cb3-9318-d4a241d8e2ed","content":"Here's the recommended setup:\n\n**1. Project file — `MyTests.csproj`**\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"MSTest.Sdk/3.7\">\n\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n\n</Project>\n```\n\nThat's it — `MSTest.Sdk` handles all the MSTest/runner references for you.\n\n**2. Enable parallel execution — `.runsettings`**\n\nCreate a `.runsettings` file at the repo root:\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <Parallelize>\n      <Workers>0</Workers>          <!-- 0 = one worker per core -->\n      <Scope>MethodLevel</Scope>    <!-- parallelize across methods -->\n    </Parallelize>\n  </MSTest>\n</RunSettings>\n```\n\nWire it up in the csproj (inside `<PropertyGroup>`):\n\n```xml\n<TestRunSettingsFile>$(MSBuildThisFileDirectory)..\\..\\.runsettings</TestRunSettingsFile>\n```\n\nOr pass it at the CLI: `dotnet test --settings .runsettings`\n\n**3. Run database tests sequentially**\n\nUse `[DoNotParallelize]` on a dedicated test class:\n\n```csharp\nusing Microsoft.VisualStudio.TestTools.UnitTesting;\n\n[TestClass]\n[DoNotParallelize]                // runs sequentially, after all parallel tests finish\npublic class DatabaseIntegrationTests\n{\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void CanInsertRecord() { /* ... */ }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void CanQueryRecords() { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n\n- **`MSTest.Sdk/3.7`** replaces all the boilerplate `PackageReference` entries (MSTest.TestFramework, MSTest.TestAdapter, coverlet, etc.).\n- **`Workers=0`** maximizes parallelism by using all available cores.\n- **`Scope=MethodLevel`** runs methods across classes in parallel (use `ClassLevel` if your tests share per-class state).\n- **`[DoNotParallelize]`** on a class pulls those tests out of the parallel pool — they run sequentially *after* all parallel tests complete. You can also put it on individual `[TestMethod]`s.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"c765ec13-4f55-4513-85c9-f2d19ee91985","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The directory is empty and there are no plugins to reference. I'll answer based on my knowledge of MSTest.Sdk, parallel execution, and sequential test control.","outputTokens":638,"requestId":"E463:2086DF:3ECA6A0:44FA437:6A02FC0B"},"id":"7a208c1e-8723-4dd9-8707-300d70194eba","timestamp":"2026-05-12T10:08:25.480Z","parentId":"5a58793d-585d-447b-b28a-049872d7c163"}
